	   <tr><td colspan=2> Well folks.. I just did this quest... First off the assassin is best found in Everfrost. exactly where the previous post says. The assassin doesnt always have the mantle. Unfortunately I have killed him 3 times and he has dropped the bloody dirk once, the mantle the other two times.. If u kill him I have found that he wont respawn for quite some time... You are better off leaving and coming back the following night.<br>  The druid, Alania, is in GF and walks the path described. I have seen Bloodbriar pop up in a different area so although they walk similar paths they dont hold the same spot.<br>  The crystal is easy. You can multiquest it with anyone of fair faction in Halas.<br>  Lastly, faction with the Tormented Soul. U wont believe this crap but I handed it in and ZIP. I conned amiable and it wasn't enough.<br>  This i really don't understand... Why do all this just to find that I'm not worthy of the mantle?? How bout not talking to me at all so I don't go shlepping all over Norrath for the pieces. If I could not use the pieces I could understand but get real Verant. The quest initiates with someone who gives me the quest! Let me finish it! sorry folks just venting.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
